You could put your shit in there.

790
00:40:49.481 --> 00:40:51.183
- Really?
- Yeah.

791
00:40:51.183 --> 00:40:53.118
Yo. that would be dope. Thank you.

792
00:40:53.118 --> 00:40:55.821
I got you.

793
00:40:55.821 --> 00:40:58.190
Look. you said you was good. but...

794
00:40:58.190 --> 00:40:59.858
I could tell there's some shit
going on up there.

795
00:40:59.858 --> 00:41:00.959
What's on your mind?

796
00:41:02.928 --> 00:41:04.462
Mm.

797
00:41:06.097 --> 00:41:08.667
'Riq. Monet wants me to give the eulogy.

798
00:41:08.667 --> 00:41:11.102
But I...

799
00:41:11.102 --> 00:41:12.737
I don't even know
how I'm supposed to speak

800
00:41:12.737 --> 00:41:14.072
at the funeral tomorrow.

801
00:41:14.072 --> 00:41:16.541
Mm.

802
00:41:16.541 --> 00:41:19.110
Yeah. I been through that.

803
00:41:19.110 --> 00:41:20.679
I mean. look. just say
what you would tell him

804
00:41:20.679 --> 00:41:22.480
if he was alive.

805
00:41:25.483 --> 00:41:27.052
Thank you.

806
00:41:28.019 --> 00:41:30.989
You got this. You tough.

807
00:41:50.508 --> 00:41:52.143
'Riq. about Effie?

808
00:41:53.278 --> 00:41:54.779
We broke up.

809
00:42:16.001 --> 00:42:18.703
You're not our usual delivery guy.

810
00:42:19.604 --> 00:42:21.606
Yeah. no. he-he called in sick.

811
00:42:22.807 --> 00:42:24.843
Okay. I'm-I'm sorry.

812
00:42:24.843 --> 00:42:27.646
Uh. you are fine as hell.

813
00:42:27.646 --> 00:42:30.315
Can I take you out?
Let me give you my digits.

814
00:42:30.548 --> 00:42:33.652
Um. they take our phones
before our shifts start.

815
00:42:33.652 --> 00:42:35.153
Oh. shit.

816
00:42:35.153 --> 00:42:37.555
Yeah. the other driver
said the same thing.

817
00:42:37.555 --> 00:42:39.057
I heard the owners are real assholes.

818
00:42:39.057 --> 00:42:40.959
Yup. One of them is getting drunk

819
00:42:40.959 --> 00:42:42.193
at the bar right now.

820
00:42:42.193 --> 00:42:44.930
I'll be cleaning puke
at opening and closing.

821
00:42:44.930 --> 00:42:46.965
Don't worry. I got you.

822
00:43:05.750 --> 00:43:08.119
Vadim. listen to me. please.

823
00:43:08.119 --> 00:43:10.055
We're losing turf!

824
00:43:10.055 --> 00:43:11.756
You need to go find us some!

825
00:43:12.223 --> 00:43:13.825
Understand?

826
00:43:13.825 --> 00:43:14.893
Yes. boss.

827
00:43:14.893 --> 00:43:16.027
Go.

828
00:43:19.364 --> 00:43:20.899
Set it in the corner

829
00:43:20.899 --> 00:43:23.635
and get the fuck out of here.

830
00:43:33.745 --> 00:43:36.614
After what you did to my father.

831
00:43:36.614 --> 00:43:38.750
I'm the only one leaving this bitch alive.

832
00:43:38.750 --> 00:43:40.085
Who the fuck are you?

833
00:43:40.085 --> 00:43:41.219
I'll show you who I am. mother--

834
00:43:42.287 --> 00:43:44.990
What the fuck is that?

835
00:43:48.693 --> 00:43:51.062
That's me. motherfucker.

836
00:43:51.062 --> 00:43:52.964
A Tejada.

837
00:43:52.964 --> 00:43:55.133
Uhh...

838
00:43:56.634 --> 00:43:57.635
Uhh--

839
00:44:00.972 --> 00:44:02.273
We out. Let's go.

840
00:44:02.273 --> 00:44:03.641
Yo. we out. Let's go. let's go!

841
00:44:08.747 --> 00:44:10.148
I need to talk to you.

842
00:44:10.148 --> 00:44:11.816
I know what you're doing
at the candy store.

843
00:44:11.816 --> 00:44:13.051
And if I know. then I'm not the only one.

844
00:44:13.051 --> 00:44:15.053
Okay. but I'm not doing that shit anymore.

845
00:44:15.053 --> 00:44:16.121
Bullshit.

846
00:44:16.121 --> 00:44:17.255
And even so. they know it's you.

847
00:44:17.255 --> 00:44:19.190
You about to get blown up...

848
00:44:19.190 --> 00:44:20.825
unless you team up with me.

849
00:44:20.825 --> 00:44:22.027
You for real?

850
00:44:22.027 --> 00:44:23.028
Absolutely.

851
00:44:24.763 --> 00:44:26.031
I'm looking for a new partner.

852
00:44:26.031 --> 00:44:27.232
and with your product and my system.

853
00:44:27.232 --> 00:44:29.034
we can keep all our shit
moving under the radar.

854
00:44:29.034 --> 00:44:31.036
Effie. naw. I don't think so.

855
00:44:31.036 --> 00:44:32.737
Just leave the thinking up to me.

856
00:44:32.737 --> 00:44:33.805
I already have it all figured out.

857
00:44:33.805 --> 00:44:35.140
I just--

858
00:44:35.140 --> 00:44:37.108
I need you to promise
not to say anything to Tariq

859
00:44:37.108 --> 00:44:38.777
until we're up and running.

860
00:44:44.382 --> 00:44:45.717
Hi. Effie.

861
00:44:50.722 --> 00:44:52.791
Fuck all y'all.

862
00:45:00.698 --> 00:45:02.267
What are you doing?

863
00:45:04.169 --> 00:45:06.337
I found an investor like
you and Uncle Lucas wanted.

864
00:45:06.337 --> 00:45:08.206
Oh. okay. that's great.

865
00:45:09.140 --> 00:45:11.109
But it's a large sum of unverifiable cash.

866
00:45:11.109 --> 00:45:14.112
not all of it. but a lot of it.

867
00:45:14.112 --> 00:45:15.447
maybe too much of it.

868
00:45:15.447 --> 00:45:17.082
Can you help me make it look legit?

869
00:45:18.116 --> 00:45:20.351
You're up to some shady shit.
Brayden. I'm not stupid.

870
00:45:20.351 --> 00:45:21.319
Okay. isn't this what you wanted?

871
00:45:21.319 --> 00:45:22.821
It's what Lucas wanted.

872
00:45:22.821 --> 00:45:23.988
You know. I didn't even tell him

873
00:45:23.988 --> 00:45:25.290
about what happened in Italy. you know.

874
00:45:25.290 --> 00:45:26.291
when you disappeared.

875
00:45:26.291 --> 00:45:27.826
And what's that?

876
00:45:27.826 --> 00:45:28.927
Okay. don't worry about it.

877
00:45:28.927 --> 00:45:30.929
It won't be like that. I promise.

878
00:45:32.430 --> 00:45:34.365
Okay.

879
00:45:34.365 --> 00:45:36.768
I can make a paper trail...

880
00:45:36.768 --> 00:45:38.136
but only if I get a cut.

881
00:45:39.104 --> 00:45:41.005
A cut?

882
00:45:41.005 --> 00:45:42.740
Who the fuck are you?

883
00:45:42.740 --> 00:45:45.243
I'm assuming risk by agreeing to help.

884
00:45:45.243 --> 00:45:47.011
You gonna give me a cut.

885
00:45:49.881 --> 00:45:50.982
Fine.

886
00:46:38.029 --> 00:46:39.430
Come on. Big Mama.

887
00:47:43.995 --> 00:47:46.431
Stand clear
of the closing doors. please.

888
00:47:52.437 --> 00:47:54.472
Where in the fuck

889
00:47:54.472 --> 00:47:56.307
do you think you are going?

890
00:48:05.149 --> 00:48:07.552
I told Noma she was crazy
for working with you kids.

891
00:48:07.552 --> 00:48:11.489
But you. you have proven yourself...

892
00:48:11.489 --> 00:48:13.091
unreliable.

893
00:48:15.393 --> 00:48:16.894
It's just product.

894
00:48:16.894 --> 00:48:18.630
Of course it's just fucking product.

895
00:48:18.630 --> 00:48:20.398
The fuck y'all thought
I was trying to do. run?

896
00:48:20.398 --> 00:48:22.000
So Noma could kill me and the last person

897
00:48:22.000 --> 00:48:23.635
- I have alive. right?
- Don't fuck with me. Tariq.

898
00:48:23.635 --> 00:48:26.471
My people tell me you're trying
to leave the country again.

899
00:48:26.471 --> 00:48:28.973
- Is that true?
- With what?

900
00:48:28.973 --> 00:48:31.075
I was going to make a drop
of your fucking product

901
00:48:31.075 --> 00:48:32.310
that you just ruined.

902
00:48:32.310 --> 00:48:33.611
So I'll be sure to mention that to Noma

903
00:48:33.611 --> 00:48:35.613
when we're short
at the next meetup. all right?

904
00:48:35.613 --> 00:48:38.383
You won't say shit to Noma.

905
00:48:39.684 --> 00:48:41.919
And you will have the full amount.

906
00:48:41.919 --> 00:48:44.555
Otherwise. you know what happens.

907
00:48:44.555 --> 00:48:46.057
Granny gets a visit.

908
00:48:47.525 --> 00:48:49.060
Just let me make the drop.

909
00:48:59.070 --> 00:49:01.105
But we will be keeping
a tighter leash on all of you

910
00:49:01.105 --> 00:49:02.473
after this little stunt--

911
00:49:02.473 --> 00:49:05.543
you. Cane. the white boy.

912
00:49:05.543 --> 00:49:07.612
and the girl.

913
00:49:07.612 --> 00:49:10.315
We can't have people thinking
you're running us.

914
00:49:10.315 --> 00:49:12.483
can we?

915
00:49:12.483 --> 00:49:14.052
And from now on.

916
00:49:14.052 --> 00:49:16.187
we need to see all of you
at these meetups.

917
00:49:16.187 --> 00:49:19.524
And alert us if you stray
from your normal course again.

918
00:49:19.524 --> 00:49:20.992
Yeah.

919
00:49:39.644 --> 00:49:42.714
Tariq. you were supposed
to be here over an hour ago.

920
00:49:42.714 --> 00:49:45.149
Yes. yes. Big Mama. I know.
I'm sorry. all right?

921
00:49:45.149 --> 00:49:46.317
I'm not gonna make it.

922
00:49:46.317 --> 00:49:48.186
I'll explain to you later. but...

923
00:49:48.186 --> 00:49:51.055
it's just not safe for you
out here anymore. all right.

924
00:49:51.055 --> 00:49:52.724
especially with you by yourself.

925
00:49:52.724 --> 00:49:55.193
So I set it up so that you
could be with Mom and Yasmine.

926
00:49:55.193 --> 00:49:57.095
Well. what about you?

927
00:49:57.095 --> 00:49:59.163
I'm working on it. Big Mama.
I'm working on it.

928
00:49:59.163 --> 00:50:01.332
Look. I just had to make sure
you were safe

929
00:50:01.332 --> 00:50:02.633
before anything else.

930
00:50:04.035 --> 00:50:06.003
Just go to Ms. Washington's office.

931
00:50:06.003 --> 00:50:07.338
This was my plan.

932
00:50:07.338 --> 00:50:09.006
She'll get you to Mom and Yas.
all right?

933
00:50:09.006 --> 00:50:13.144
No. Tariq. I am not
leaving you here alone.

934
00:50:13.144 --> 00:50:14.379
Big Mama. trust me.

935
00:50:14.379 --> 00:50:17.215
This is exactly what I need. all right?

936
00:50:19.016 --> 00:50:21.285
I'm sorry for everything.

937
00:50:21.285 --> 00:50:24.021
Look. just tell Ma and Yas
that I love them.

938
00:50:24.021 --> 00:50:26.691
And I'll be back with you guys
as soon as I can. all right?

939
00:50:26.691 --> 00:50:28.092
I promise.

940
00:50:30.361 --> 00:50:32.630
Damn it.

941
00:51:20.578 --> 00:51:23.147
While society may have told Lorenzo Tejada

942
00:51:23.147 --> 00:51:25.783
that he meant nothing to them.

943
00:51:25.783 --> 00:51:28.753
to our family. he was the world.

944
00:51:30.221 --> 00:51:32.223
He was our world.

945
00:51:34.826 --> 00:51:36.294
Not yet.

946
00:51:36.294 --> 00:51:38.129
We need more leverage before we move in.

947
00:51:38.129 --> 00:51:39.397
I agree.

948
00:51:39.397 --> 00:51:41.732
Let's see what else those cameras catch.

949
00:51:48.473 --> 00:51:49.807
I know I let you down. Pops.

950
00:51:52.143 --> 00:51:54.412
That'll never happen again.

951
00:51:54.412 --> 00:51:55.513
Family first.

952
00:52:29.180 --> 00:52:30.181
Now!

953
00:52:44.362 --> 00:52:45.796
Who the fuck is shooting at us?

954
00:52:45.796 --> 00:52:46.797
The Russians.

955
00:52:46.797 --> 00:52:48.699
Hey. yo. post up.

956
00:52:50.234 --> 00:52:51.669
Now!

957
00:53:07.418 --> 00:53:08.753
You got us in a fucking war?

958
00:53:08.753 --> 00:53:10.555
Nigga. is you out your motherfucking mind?

959
00:53:10.555 --> 00:53:12.757
You might be rocking Papi's piece.

960
00:53:12.757 --> 00:53:15.426
but I'm stepping up to number one.

961
00:53:15.426 --> 00:53:16.627
What you say?
- Hit me. bitch--

962
00:53:16.627 --> 00:53:17.862
Hey. stop. Dru. fall back.

963
00:53:17.862 --> 00:53:19.463
Stand down. Cane.

964
00:53:19.463 --> 00:53:20.965
None of us got shot. all right?

965
00:53:21.198 --> 00:53:23.234
Dru had a plan. He made the right call.

966
00:53:43.988 --> 00:53:46.724
What do you want? I'm busy.

967
00:53:46.724 --> 00:53:48.626
Busy doing what?

968
00:53:49.527 --> 00:53:50.828
Burning Tariq's shit down.

969
00:53:50.828 --> 00:53:52.430
You wanna fuck with me. that's cool.

970
00:53:52.430 --> 00:53:54.498
But I'm out to show him who
the fuck built this coffee app

971
00:53:54.498 --> 00:53:55.967
- in the first place.
- Wait. wait. wait. hold up.

972
00:53:55.967 --> 00:53:58.502
Hold up. hold up. Gotta chill.

973
00:53:58.502 --> 00:54:00.771
Did you really just touch my shit?

974
00:54:00.771 --> 00:54:03.240
I get that you wanna fuck this nigga up.

975
00:54:03.240 --> 00:54:04.475
You did what his bitch ass couldn't.

976
00:54:04.475 --> 00:54:05.643
I woulda did the same thing.

977
00:54:07.712 --> 00:54:08.913
I know.

978
00:54:08.913 --> 00:54:11.983
But crashing this app
won't just hurt Tariq.

979
00:54:11.983 --> 00:54:14.819
- It'll destroy all of us.
- Okay. and what about it?

980
00:54:21.258 --> 00:54:23.661
What if I gave you a better solution?

981
00:54:26.397 --> 00:54:27.965
I'll slide you some product.

982
00:54:27.965 --> 00:54:29.400
You keep your hustle.

983
00:54:29.400 --> 00:54:30.868
Tariq never has to know.

984
00:54:32.370 --> 00:54:34.705
Why would you do that. Cane?

985
00:54:34.705 --> 00:54:37.608
You shouldn't be punished
for handling business.

986
00:54:38.643 --> 00:54:42.647
Besides. you looked out for me
with that wire shit. so...

987
00:54:42.647 --> 00:54:44.382
I wanna look out for you.

988
00:55:00.731 --> 00:55:02.533
Didn't expect to hear from you.

989
00:55:02.533 --> 00:55:04.669
Yeah. well. shit's out
of my control right now.

990
00:55:04.669 --> 00:55:06.737
Fucking Obi screwed me up.

991
00:55:06.737 --> 00:55:08.873
- Shit.
- Mm-hmm.

992
00:55:08.873 --> 00:55:10.374
All right. no matter

993
00:55:10.374 --> 00:55:11.676
what the fucking circumstances are.

994
00:55:11.676 --> 00:55:13.577
me and you both know we need
each other to stay alive.

995
00:55:13.577 --> 00:55:15.646
So if we wanna move forward.

996
00:55:15.646 --> 00:55:19.517
we gotta figure out a way to
get out from under Noma asap.

997
00:55:19.517 --> 00:55:21.052
I assume you have a plan?

998
00:55:21.052 --> 00:55:22.553
Look. Effie got this picture in Italy.

999
00:55:22.553 --> 00:55:24.321
And I think that could be
our leverage to get out.

1000
00:55:24.321 --> 00:55:28.092
But the thing is.
it might take a minute to get.

1001
00:55:28.325 --> 00:55:29.960
And on top of that. we gotta
move drugs in the meantime

1002
00:55:29.960 --> 00:55:31.462
for Noma so we don't all die.

1003
00:55:31.462 --> 00:55:33.030
so I need back in the building.

1004
00:55:33.030 --> 00:55:35.433
and you need to show up
to these meetings. all right?

1005
00:55:35.433 --> 00:55:37.068
All right. Say less.

1006
00:56:09.600 --> 00:56:11.502
The feds roped up the Russians.

1007
00:56:11.502 --> 00:56:13.771
Your family's safe... for now.

1008
00:56:13.771 --> 00:56:16.741
But I would lay low just in case.

1009
00:56:16.741 --> 00:56:18.709
Got it. Thanks.

1010
00:56:24.715 --> 00:56:26.917
It's too bad.

1011
00:56:26.917 --> 00:56:28.419
I loved you.

1012
00:56:29.587 --> 00:56:33.791
Even after what you did. I still love you.

1013
00:56:37.561 --> 00:56:39.964
They're gonna figure it out. Mo.

1014
00:56:41.699 --> 00:56:43.000
And when they do...

1015
00:56:46.670 --> 00:56:49.774
...those kids are never gonna forgive you.
